      (őľ := őľ) (őĹ := őĹ) (cell := cell) hcell hdisj hzero Finset.univ)

/--
Durrett 2019, Example 4.3.7 generator-facing endpoint: if a finite
partition-generated pi-system consists of finite unions of the cells, then the
