theorem
    durrett2019_theorem_4_5_7_runningAbsMax_lintegral_le_terminal_tail_add_min_terminal_lintegral_of_source_square_minus_martingale_monotone_terminal
    {ő© : Type*} [mő© : MeasurableSpace ő©]
